Xin chào.

583
01:17:24,445 --> 01:17:25,486
Em khỏe chứ?

584
01:17:26,569 --> 01:17:28,434
Em khỏe.

585
01:17:29,643 --> 01:17:30,799
Chuyện gì vậy?

586
01:17:31,456 --> 01:17:36,425
